name: LumberJack (Cartraige)
description: Survival Game. Defeat the Orge Boss to win the game. Don't use up all of your fire wood, save it for the winters. Don't let your Camp fire die out or you loose. The blue fire heals you and the red one gives you power, rage, speed and also the ability to throw your axe (super powerful move). Good Luck and choose between health or power.
